"position":18,"arabic":"٥","translation":"(৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":6,"arabic":"ثُمَّ رَدَدْنَا لَكُمُ ٱلْكَرَّةَ عَلَيْهِمْ وَأَمْدَدْنَٰكُم بِأَمْوَٰلٍۢ وَبَنِينَ وَجَعَلْنَٰكُمْ أَكْثَرَ نَفِيرًا","translation":"And after a time We allowed you to prevail against them once again, and aided you with wealth and offspring, and made you more numerous [than ever].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2035.mp3","surahId":17,"words":[{"id":5866,"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/017_006_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5867,"position":2,"arabic":"رَدَدْنَا","translation":"আমরা ফিরিয়ে দিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/017_006_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5868,"position":3,"arabic":"لَكُمُ","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/017_006_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5869,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْكَرَّةَ","translation":"পালা","audioUrl":"wbw/017_006_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5870,"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","translation":"উপর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/017_006_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5871,"position":6,"arabic":"وَأَمْدَدْنَـٰكُم","translation":"এবং আমরা সাহায্য করলাম তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/017_006_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5872,"position":7,"arabic":"بِأَمْوَٰلٍۢ","translation":"দিয়ে সম্পদসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/017_006_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5873,"position":8,"arabic":"وَبَنِينَ","translation":"ও সন্তানাদি (দিয়ে)","audioUrl":"wbw/017_006_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5874,"position":9,"arabic":"وَجَعَلْنَـٰكُمْ","translation":"এবং আমরা পরিণত করলাম তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/017_006_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5875,"position":10,"arabic":"أَكْثَرَ","translation":"গরিষ্ঠ","audioUrl":"wbw/017_006_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5876,"position":11,"arabic":"نَفِيرًا","translation":"সংখ্যায়","audioUrl":"wbw/017_006_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5877,"position":12,"arabic":"٦","translation":"(৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":7,"arabic":"إِنْ أَحْسَنتُمْ أَحْسَنتُمْ لِأَنفُسِكُمْ ۖ وَإِنْ أَسَأْتُمْ فَلَهَا ۚ فَإِذَا جَآءَ وَعْدُ ٱلْءَاخِرَةِ لِيَسُۥٓـُٔوا۟ وُجُوهَكُمْ وَلِيَدْخُلُوا۟ ٱلْمَسْجِدَ كَمَا دَخَلُوهُ أَوَّلَ مَرَّةٍۢ وَلِيُتَبِّرُوا۟ مَا عَلَوْا۟ تَتْبِيرًا","translation":"[And We said:] \"If you persevere in doing good, you will but be doing good to yourselves; and if you do evil, it will be [done] to yourselves.\" And so, when the prediction of the second [period of your iniquity] came true, [We raised new enemies against you, and allowed them] to disgrace you utterly, and to enter the Temple as [their forerunners] had entered it once before, and to destroy with utter destruction all that they had conquered.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2036.mp3","surahId":17,"words":[{"id":7166,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنْ","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/017_007_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7167,"position":2,"arabic":"أَحْسَنتُمْ","translation":"ভালো কাজ করে থাকো তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/017_007_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7168,"position":3,"arabic":"أَحْسَنتُمْ","translation":"ভালো কাজ করেছো তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/017_007_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7169,"position":4,"arabic":"لِأَنفُسِكُمْ ۖ","translation":"জন্যে নিজেদের তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/017_007_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7171,"position":5,"arabic":"وَإِنْ","translation":"আর যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/017_007_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7172,"position":6,"arabic":"أَسَأْتُمْ","translation":"মন্দ কাজ করে থাকো তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/017_007_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7173,"position":7,"arabic":"فَلَهَا ۚ","translation":"জন্যে তাও নিজেদের","audioUrl":"wbw/017_007_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7175,"position":8,"arabic":"فَإِذَا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/017_007_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7176,"position":9,"arabic":"جَآءَ","translation":"আসলো","au